                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890909-106-off528 t17890909-106-cd529"></join> last, one watch, with the inside case made of metal, and the outside case covered with shagreen, value 20 s. one seal, value 6 d. one key, value 3 d. one string, value 3 d.
